                <li>Enjoy personalized itineraries for groups or solo riders.</li>
                <li>Immerse yourself in local culture and sights along the way.</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/register-custom-tour" class="block bg-red-500 text-white text-center py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-black transition duration-300">
                Start Planning Your Tour
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
